data.title: Carlsbad Meeting Rooms & Event Spaces
data.meta_description: Browse our meeting rooms at K1 Speed Carlsbad. These private spaces are perfect for birthday parties, company events, and other special occasions.
data.text:
Meeting spaces are now available for rent “a la carte” without an accompanying Race Package purchase.

All meeting rooms can be rented hourly or at discounted rates for half and whole days.

Please email Group Sales for more info, or call 1-855-517-7333.
